{"tha-ap157:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap157:0.2":"Bandhujivakavagga ","tha-ap157:0.3":"5 Mandaravapupphapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap157:1.1":"“Devaputto aham santo, ","tha-ap157:1.2":"pujayim sikhinayakam; ","tha-ap157:1.3":"Mandaravena pupphena, ","tha-ap157:1.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap157:2.1":"Sattaham chadanam asi, ","tha-ap157:2.2":"dibbam malam tathagate; ","tha-ap157:2.3":"Sabbe jana samagantva, ","tha-ap157:2.4":"namassimsu tathagatam. ","tha-ap157:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap157:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap157:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap157:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap157:4.1":"Ito ca dasame kappe, ","tha-ap157:4.2":"rajahosim jutindharo; ","tha-ap157:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap157:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap157:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap157:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap157:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap157:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mandaravapupphapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap157:7.1":"Mandaravapupphapujakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}